ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T06:27:45.000Z","msg":"閱讀攞U?<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> 她只好考慮求助<span style=\"color: red;\">大阪中國領事館</span></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T06:29:22.000Z","msg":"屌，以為你講條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a83690a01e09c79bfb225e5e6534bf82d7c1246","tid":674906,"uid":2267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"上年去大阪心齋橋裡面某間藥妝店買嘢，埋單時去退稅櫃位，我畀本BNO佢，條店員（大陸女）用普通話同我講：我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，店員大陸女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：香港人？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：香港回歸了支那，為什麼不拿支那護照或特衰護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時我都呆呆，咁都同我講政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我直接屌佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：支那女人嚟日本打工留學做乜撚嘢？做乜鳩唔死返去支那？<br />\n南方口音嘅普通話，10個有7-8個都識廣東話<br />\n條大陸女扮攰然後同佢同事講要休息陣，走鬼咗，搞到我戇鳩鳩等咗陣先有人埋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11b502bf77e2441eb99fe2bcd30a335c6c9634e","tid":674906,"uid":12879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"地獄鬼國"},{"pid":"810cf830be39b5d84c5b6a19c6d7355bb5c04f85","tid":674906,"ui